      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my dad just got in from his flight from tokyo. he's saying his left arm feels kinda heavy and tingly like it's falling asleep, and he sounds a bit weird when he talks, like his speech is thick or something. he thinks he's just really exhausted from the long flight though. do u think he just needs to sleep it off?",
