      "content": "he's really insistent though, he says he's just super dehydrated and jet lagged and doesn't want to deal with an ambulance/hospital at this hour. if i just give him some electrolytes and let him nap for a few hours, that should be fine right? he's always been a bit dramatic about these things.",
